      <title>台湾以安全风险为由建议总统不要访问南海</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/citing-safety-risk-taiwan-recommends-president-does-not-visit-schina-sea-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高安全官员周四表示，他目前不建议蔡英文总统访问南海，因为她的飞行可能面临“有关国家干涉”的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/citing-safety-risk-taiwan-recommends-president-does-not-visit-schina-sea-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰间谍机构审查建议对其托管的任何外国合作伙伴能力进行审计</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-spy-agency-review-suggests-audit-any-foreign-partner-capabilities-it-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对新西兰一家间谍机构的审查表明，在对其托管外国信号情报系统进行调查后，该机构需要对其可能为其他国家运营的任何能力进行审核。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-spy-agency-review-suggests-audit-any-foreign-partner-capabilities-it-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:26:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国坚持降息计划亚洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，在美联储表示将坚持降息计划后，亚洲股市反弹，金价和日本日经指数跃升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着就业复苏，澳大利亚二月份失业率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australian-jobless-rate-dives-feb-employment-resurgent-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2月份澳大利亚就业大幅反弹，而失业率则远低于预期，这明显表明劳动力市场仍然紧张，而且近期的疲软状况在统计上被夸大了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australian-jobless-rate-dives-feb-employment-resurgent-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国外交官卢敦促巴基斯坦调查选举，可能重新进行一些投票</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-diplomat-lu-urges-pakistan-probe-election-possibly-re-run-some-votes-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国外交官周三敦促巴基斯坦调查上个月大选中报道的违规行为，如果发现可靠的干扰证据，则在受影响的选区重新进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-diplomat-lu-urges-pakistan-probe-election-possibly-re-run-some-votes-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:04:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国回击美国批评香港新国安法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hits-back-us-criticising-new-hong-kong-security-law-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周四表示，对美方对本周早些时候通过的香港新国安法的“诋毁和抹黑”表示强烈不满和坚决反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hits-back-us-criticising-new-hong-kong-security-law-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:58:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美联储坚持到底，美元下跌；澳元因就业数据而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-slips-fed-stays-course-aussie-jumps-jobs-data-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对通胀意外上行，美联储维持今年降息预期，并没有像一些投资者担心的那样采取更强硬的基调，美元周四普遍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-slips-fed-stays-course-aussie-jumps-jobs-data-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大称香港新国安法不保障人权</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-says-hong-kongs-new-security-law-does-not-safeguard-human-rights-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大周三表示，香港新的国家安全法“未能保障”人权和基本自由，并与欧盟、美国、英国和联合国一起对该立法提出批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-says-hong-kongs-new-security-law-does-not-safeguard-human-rights-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚与英国加强防务合作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-uk-sign-new-defence-pact-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚和英国周四签署了一项新的国防和安全合作协议，使两国国防军更容易在彼此国家共同行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-uk-sign-new-defence-pact-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:33:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据彭博社报道，斯里兰卡将于下周开始与投资者进行重组谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week-bloomberg-news-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社周四报道，全球投资者和斯里兰卡官员预计下周将启动旨在重组 120 亿美元违约全球债券的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sri-lanka-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week-bloomberg-news-2024-03-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 21:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
